'''''Stomper One''''' was a [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] [[Assault shuttle/Legends|assault shuttle]] used by [[Grand Master/Legends|Grand Master]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and his party of [[YVH-Series battle droid|YVH]] to retake the [[Admiral Ackbar (Victory-class)|''Admiral Ackbar'']] from the [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] at the [[Battle of Tenupe]]. ''Stomper One'' was destroyed by [[Raynar Thul]] via [[The Force/Legends|the Force]], however, Skywalker survived as well as the Bugcrunchers and successfully completed the mission in retaking the ship.

